#. Translators: Summary/title for this add-on
#. to be shown on installation and add-on information found in add-on store
msgid "LINE Desktop Accessibility"
msgstr "LINE 電腦版無障礙增強"

#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-on store
msgid ""
"Enhances NVDA accessibility support for the LINE desktop application on "
"Windows.\n"
"Provides improved navigation for chat lists, messages, contacts, and message "
"input.\n"
"Supports voice and video calls, incoming call handling, microphone and "
"camera status announcements, and OCR-assisted text reading."
msgstr ""
"增強 NVDA 對 Windows 上 LINE 電腦版應用程式的無障礙支援。\n"
"提供對聊天列表、訊息、聯絡人和訊息輸入的改進導覽體驗。\n"
"支援語音與視訊通話、來電處理、麥克風與相機狀態播報，以及 OCR 輔助文字閱讀。"

#. Translators: what's new content for the add-on version to be shown in the add-on store
msgid ""
"Improved video call handling and incoming call detection.\n"
"Added microphone and camera status announcements during calls.\n"
"Added Focus Call Window shortcut (NVDA+Windows+F).\n"
"Improved message copy-read reliability."
msgstr ""
"改善視訊通話處理與來電偵測。\n"
"新增通話中麥克風與相機狀態播報功能。\n"
"新增跳到通話視窗快速鍵（NVDA+Windows+F）。\n"
"改善訊息複製閱讀的穩定性。"

